I"L3<h1 class="no_toc" id="tests-for-just-the-docs">Tests for Just the Docs</h1>

<p>Various <a href="docs/">tests</a> illustrate how the theme renders various elements.</p>

<p>The following sections are a log of the creation of this website, with links to some relevant resources.</p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/pdmosses/just-the-docs-tests/issues">Bug reports and suggestions for improvement</a> are welcome!</p>

